bout 2 hours and 2 minutes, DTLX for roughly 2 hours and 14 minutes, the telegram:group session for about 1 hour and 48 minutes, and the current cron session started just moments ago with zero elapsed time.\n\nThere's also a stale QLHV report session that started around 11:43 UTC and hasn't seen any activity in about an hour, so I'll mark it as inactive. Now I'm composing the status message to send to the Lead.","thinkingSignature":"fa564965287741c95436f201b806a9e2b18465c4f4d1304b503b894af3f386db"},{"type":"text","text":"Now I'll compile the status and send it to Lead. I see 4 other active sessions (excluding this cron session), plus 1 stale pre-existing session.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wrrzxd2j3ix7_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","agentId":"master-orchestrator","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 12:44 UTC 14 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 5\n• cron:6f3323ef (5p DTLX): running — 5-minute progress monitoring (DTLX ecosystem) — ~2h 14m\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (5p QLHV): running — 5-minute progress monitoring (QLHV ecosystem) — ~2h 2m\n• telegram:group:-5163901258: running — Telegram group session (AHV QLHV ecosystem) — ~1h 48m\n• cron:e7885813 (Agent Status): running — this status check to Lead — just now\n• cron:b653a6c0 (QLHV Report): stale — pre-existing zombie, last activity ~11:43 UTC — ~1h 1m\n\nPipeline: Healthy ✅ No blockers. All cron monitors stable.\n— Orbis 🌐"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":6297,"output":835,"cacheRead":13849,"cacheWrite":303,"totalTokens":21284,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776170698848,"responseId":"062d69cbd08385250fab795adb2b6792"}}
